00:25:40.150 --> 00:25:42.260
And this is the kind
of nonsense that's

00:25:42.260 --> 00:25:44.820
actually going on in this
country and all over the world.

00:25:47.610 --> 00:25:50.010
This is not science the way
it's supposed to be done.

00:25:50.010 --> 00:25:53.050
And DNA got a pass when the
National Academy of Sciences

00:25:53.050 --> 00:25:55.654
looked at all of the
forensic sciences.

00:25:55.654 --> 00:25:56.820
They didn't like bite marks.

00:25:56.820 --> 00:25:58.295
They criticized
fingerprints because they

00:25:58.295 --> 00:25:59.211
