00:25:59.211 --> 00:25:59.900
They love DNA.

00:25:59.900 --> 00:26:04.080
And I was just very upset
that day when that came out.

00:26:04.080 --> 00:26:07.250
So out of those
labs, 76 of the 108

00:26:07.250 --> 00:26:09.010
