00:28:35.100 --> 00:28:38.650
So here's again a case
where you have a DNA match.

00:28:38.650 --> 00:28:39.490
It looks good.

00:28:39.490 --> 00:28:41.150
It looked good even to me.

00:28:41.150 --> 00:28:42.330
The full kit was used.

