00:39:30.792 --> 00:39:32.500
I think there's a lot
a mixup being done.

00:39:32.500 --> 00:39:34.900
And the tragic thing about
those is there's no way to tell.

00:39:34.900 --> 00:39:37.275
There's nothing I can do for
